# CUSTOM BASH COLOR
# 30m - Black
# 31m - Red
# 32m - Green
# 33m - Yellow
# 34m - Blue
# 35m - Purple
# 36m - Cyan
# 37m - White
# 40m - Background Black
# 41m - Background Red
# 42m - Background Green
# 43m - Background Yellow
# 44m - Background Blue
# 45m - Background Purple
# 46m - Background Cyan
# 47m - Background White
# 0 - Normal
# 1 - Bold

